data.eml:eml: Three new species of Psilorhynchus from the Ayeyarwaddy River drainage, Myanmar (Teleostei: Psilorhynchidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Conway, Kevin W., Britz, Ralf (2010): Three new species of Psilorhynchus from the Ayeyarwaddy River drainage, Myanmar (Teleostei: Psilorhynchidae). Zootaxa 2616: 31-47, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.197944
